sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant F as Flutter App
  participant FA as Firebase Auth
  participant B as Sport Energy API
  participant D as MongoDB

  U->>F: Register with email and password
  F->>FA: Create Firebase account
  FA-->>F: Firebase ID token and UID
  F->>B: Create pending user with Firebase ID token
  B->>FA: Verify token with Firebase Admin
  B->>D: Store Firebase UID and PENDING_EMAIL status
  B-->>F: Registration accepted
  F->>FA: Send email-verification link
  FA-->>U: Firebase verification email
  U->>FA: Open verification link
  U->>F: Return to app
  F->>FA: Reload current user
  FA-->>F: emailVerified equals true
  F->>B: Confirm verification with fresh Firebase ID token
  B->>FA: Verify token and email_verified claim
  B->>D: Activate user
  B-->>F: App session tokens
